<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd">
<html><head><meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /><style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style></head><body style=" font-family:'.SF NS Text'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p align="center" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">簡介</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（太 4:4）耶穌卻回答說：「〔經上〕記着說： 人活着，不是單靠食物， 乃是靠上帝口裏所出的一切話。」</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（來 4:12）上帝的道是活潑的，是有功效的，比一切兩刃的劍更快，甚至魂與靈，骨節與骨髓，都能刺入、剖開，連心中的思念和主意都能辨明。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（詩 119:105）你的話是我腳前的燈， 是我路上的光。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（詩 18:28）你必點着我的燈； 耶和華－我的上帝必照明我的黑暗。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（詩 19:8）耶和華的訓詞正直，能快活人的心； 耶和華的命令清潔，能明亮人的眼目。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（賽 40:8）草必枯乾，花必凋殘， 惟有我們上帝的話必永遠立定。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">（彼前 1:25）惟有主的道是永存的。 所傳給你們的福音就是這道。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Kaiti TC';">神的話語，帶有能力，永恆不變。這小本子選錄了一些您或身邊的人可能遇到的情況，並編錄了相對的回應經文，旨在鼓勵主內的弟兄姊妹，不論任何處境都要依靠神的話語。生活或會遇到不同的挑戰，但神的愛和應許永不改變。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Times'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri,sans-serif';">--------------------------------------------------</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p align="center" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p align="center" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">你的話是我腳前的燈，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">是我路上的光。</span> </p>
<p align="center" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 119:105</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#000000;">當你害怕時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（賽</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 41:10</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你不要害怕，因為我與你同在；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">不要驚惶，因為我是你的上帝。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我必堅固你，我必幫助你；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我必用我公義的右手扶持你。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（申</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 31:8</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）耶和華必在你前面行；他必與你同在，必不撇下你，也不丟棄你。不要懼怕，也不要驚惶。」</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（太</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 10:30</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）就是你們的頭髮也都被數過了。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#000000;">當你憂慮時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（箴</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';">10:22</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）耶和華所賜的福使人富足，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">並不加上憂慮。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（腓</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:6</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）應當一無掛慮，只要凡事藉着禱告、祈求，和感謝，將你們所要的告訴上帝。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（太</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 6:25-34</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）「所以我告訴你們，不要為生命憂慮吃甚麼，喝甚麼；為身體憂慮穿甚麼。生命不勝於飲食嗎？身體不勝於衣裳嗎？</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（路</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 1:46-47</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）馬利亞說：</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我心尊主為大；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（彼前</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 5:7</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你們要將一切的憂慮卸給上帝，因為他顧念你們。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">55:22</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你要把你的重擔卸給耶和華，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">他必撫養你；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">他永不叫義人動搖。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 46</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）上帝是我們的避難所，是我們的力量，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">是〔我們〕在患難中隨時的幫助。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">當你失落時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 42:5</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我的心哪，你為何憂悶？</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">為何在我裏面煩躁？</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">應當仰望上帝，因他笑臉幫助我；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我還要稱讚他。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（來</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:16</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）所以，我們只管坦然無懼地來到施恩的寶座前，為要得憐恤，蒙恩惠，作隨時的幫助。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（羅</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:17-21</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）亞伯拉罕所信的，是那叫死人復活、使無變為有的上帝，他在主面前作我們世人的父。如〔經上〕所記：「我已經立你作多國的父。」</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（何</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 6:3</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我們務要認識耶和華，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">竭力追求認識他。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">他出現確如晨〔光〕；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">他必臨到我們像甘雨，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">像滋潤田地的春雨。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">當你面臨危機時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 121</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我要向山舉目；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我的幫助從何而來？</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 28:7</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）耶和華是我的力量，是我的盾牌；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我心裏倚靠他就得幫助。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">所以我心中歡樂，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我必用詩歌頌讚他。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（林後</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 3:17</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）主就是那靈；主的靈在哪裏，那裏就得以自由。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（提後</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 1:7</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）因為上帝賜給我們，不是膽怯的心，乃是剛強、仁愛、謹守的心。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#000000;">當你灰心時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（加</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 6:9</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我們行善，不可喪志；若不灰心，到了時候就要收成。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（賽</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 40:8</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）草必枯乾，花必凋殘，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">惟有我們上帝的話必永遠立定。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（林後</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:8-18</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我們四面受敵，卻不被困住；心裏作難，卻不致失望；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（腓</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:4-7</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你們要靠主常常喜樂。我再說，你們要喜樂。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（約一</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 1:8</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我們若說自己無罪，便是自欺，真理不在我們心裏了。</span> </p>
