<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 23:4</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我雖然行過死蔭的〔幽〕谷，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">也不怕遭害，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">因為你與我同在；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">你的杖，你的竿，都安慰我。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（羅</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 8:38-39</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）因為我深信無論是死，是生，是天使，是掌權的，是有能的，是現在的事，是將來的事，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（約一</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:16</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）上帝愛我們的心，我們也知道也信。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">上帝就是愛；住在愛裏面的，就是住在上帝裏面，上帝也住在他裏面。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#000000;">當你遇到不公平時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 12:5</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）耶和華說：因為困苦人的冤屈</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">和貧窮人的歎息，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我現在要起來，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">把他安置在他所切慕的穩妥之地。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 92:7</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）惡人茂盛如草，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">一切作孽之人發旺的時候，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">正是他們要滅亡，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">直到永遠。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（羅</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';">12:19</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）親愛的弟兄，不要自己伸冤，寧可讓步，聽憑主怒〔註：或譯：讓人發怒〕；因為〔經上〕記着：「主說：『伸冤在我，我必報應。』」</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（箴</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';">4:23</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你要保守你心，勝過保守一切〔註：或譯：你要切切保守你心〕，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">因為一生的果效是由心發出。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（箴</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 16:2</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）人一切所行的，在自己眼中看為清潔；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">惟有耶和華衡量人心。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#000000;">當你疲乏時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 68:9</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）上帝啊，你降下大雨；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">你產業〔以色列〕疲乏的時候，你使他堅固。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（賽</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 40:29</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）疲乏的，他賜能力；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">軟弱的，他加力量。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（耶</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 31:25</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）疲乏的人，我使他飽飫；愁煩的人，我使他知足。」</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（太</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 11:28-29</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）凡勞苦擔重擔的人可以到我這裏來，我就使你們得安息。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#000000;">當你缺乏時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 23</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）耶和華是我的牧者，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我必不致缺乏。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 1:3</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）他要像一棵樹栽在溪水旁，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">按時候結果子，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">葉子也不枯乾。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">凡他所做的盡都順利。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（腓</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:19</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我的上帝必照他榮耀的豐富，在基督耶穌裏，使你們一切所需用的都充足。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（來</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 13:5-6</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你們存心不可貪愛錢財，要以自己所有的為足；因為主曾說：「我總不撇下你，也不丟棄你。」</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">當你被背叛時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（創</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 12:3</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）為你祝福的，我必賜福與他；那咒詛你的，我必咒詛他。地上的萬族都要因你得福。」</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（箴</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 19:5</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）作假見證的，必不免受罰；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">吐出謊言的，終不能逃脫。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（路</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 17:3-4</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你們要謹慎！若是你的弟兄得罪〔你〕，就勸戒他；他若懊悔，就饒恕他。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（羅</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 12:14-21</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）逼迫你們的，要給他們祝福；只要祝福，不可咒詛。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 41:9-13</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）連我知己的朋友，</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">我所倚靠、吃過我飯的也用腳踢我。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">當你遇到試探時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（林前</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 10:13</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你們所遇見的試探，無非是人所能受的。上帝是信實的，必不叫你們受試探過於所能受的；在受試探的時候，總要給你們開一條出路，叫你們能忍受得住。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（太</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 4:1-11</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）當時，耶穌被〔聖〕靈引到曠野，受魔鬼的試探。</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;">…</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi';">加</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> 5:16</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我說，你們當順着〔聖〕靈而行，就不放縱肉體的情慾了。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">當你迷失時</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（彼前</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 2:25</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）你們從前好像迷路的羊，如今卻歸到你們靈魂的牧人監督了。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（詩</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 25:14</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）耶和華與敬畏他的人親密；</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">他必將自己的約指示他們。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（約</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 10:27</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）我的羊聽我的聲音，我也認識他們，他們也跟着我。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">（約一</span><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif'; color:#000000;"> 2:6</span><span style=" font-family:'KaiTi'; color:#000000;">）人若說他住在主裏面，就該自己照主所行的去行。</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Calibri Light,sans-serif';"> </span> </p></body></html>